

GOALS

X Basic 3D first-person environment
- Player pickup element
- Player "discovers" new element upon pickup
- Player place element
- Player able to retrieve known elements (element vault UI)
- Player interact with burner aparatus
- Player place element in burner aparatus
- Active burner aparatus tranforms element
- Element web definition
- Use element web during gameplay to inform what happens to elements under the 
    right conditions
- 'N' number elements discoverable (decide on a decent prototype number)